column4: ok, so let's say you don't now about whether or not reiser4 is on the new live cd. can you at least point me in the direction of a complete package list?
If they don't have the list on ubuntu-linux.org, you can always just download the ISO and take a peek
Well, if no one here knows, you could either try google, or try again later.
Devs hang around in here, I think, but they're apparently all away at the moment.  You *could* try #ubuntu-dev, but I don't know if they'd like you doing that.
